donor_name: UNDP AS ADMINISTRATIVE AGENT FOR A JOINT PROGRAMME PASS THROUGH ARRANGEMENT
outputs.output_descr: Capacity development of the House of Representatives.

Orientation Programme for the new National Assembly  of Tanzania and the Zanzibar House of Representatives in the context of the Government of the National Unity held; Standing Orders of the Zanzibar House of Representatives revised and passed by the House in-line with the requirements of the Government of National Unity; Legislature Support Project (LSP) document drafted and approved; and the LSP operational.
